					<div class="static-page-text">
						<p>Forrest Fenn's <%= link_to "book", "http://www.collectedworksbookstore.com/product/thrill-chase-forrest-fenn", target: "_blank" %> and <%= link_to "website", "http://www.oldsantafetradingco.com/the-thrill-resource-page", target: "_blank" %> introduce the poem with slightly different sentences. 
