					<div class="static-page-text">
						<p>1. In the book version of the poem, this word is "answers"; in the online version of the poem the word is "answer".
							In response to someone who wrote to him about this discrepancy, <%= link_to "Fenn replied", "http://dalneitzel.com/2013/06/19/forrest-gets-mail-4/", target: "_blank" %>, "It makes no difference, one of them is only an innocent typo. You can pick which one. f"
							<%= link_to "[return]", "#answers" %>
						</p>
